      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a museum-quality E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six utilizing individual throttle bodies and double VANOS for immediate throttle response. This example features a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential with zero lash. Mechanically optimized with documented rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe, the chassis remains factory-stiff. The suspension geometry is dialed, offering exceptional turn-in and poise. This is a pristine, turn-key specimen for the purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
